data.title: Camila (TV series)
data.meta_description: Camila is a Mexican telenovela produced by Angelli Nesma Medina for Televisa in 1998. The story is a remake of 1978 Mexican telenovela Viviana. It aired on Canal de Las Estrellas from September 14, 1998 to January 15, 1999.
